text.section:
After the conversion is approved under subsection (2) of this section, the converting organization shall deliver to the Secretary of State for filing a certificate of trust which satisfies the requirements of KRS 386A.2-010 and includes as well:
A statement that the converting organization was converted to a statutory trust;
The former name of the converting organization;
The form of organization of the converting organization prior to the conversion; and
A statement that the conversion was approved in accordance with subsection (2) of this section.
